title: [YTP] Hot Erotic Nut Job Action
description:
Turner Movie Classics (no affiliation) would be proud to present "Hot Erotic Nut Job Action," an artistically rendered film set in the repressive era of 1959 Oakton, CO. A lonely squirrel lashes out against the isolation inherent in society and endures numerous scarring hardships to learn how homosexual love can pierce through the curtain of totalitarianism in this pre-modern allegory for North Korean fascism. Along the way, he discovers the inconvenient truth that unrequited romance is never as romantic as it seems. 

The second episode of the first season of popular television series "YouTube Poop", the original film was lost in a canister lodged up Bill Paxton's left nostril. It was then used by a little old lady from Slaughter, ME to do her Sunday shopping until the fall of the Brisbane Empire to the NY Met Sox. In a few moments, the results of that trial.
